N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 5613.1 - Commission authority

State Regulations

The commission may impose on any person, including an
entity, any penalty or sanction authorized by the Racing, Pari-Mutuel Wagering
and Breeding Law or this Chapter. Notes
